      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FAYE VALENTINE (6) was in the placings last time but shapes well for this on her slick win the start prior, getting around Warrnambool over 390m in 22.16. Has the ability and expected to go close again. AUSSIE WAGYU (3) settled down midfield and held his position to the line when finishing 4th (22.47) at Ballarat. Returns to favourable track. Got the money at his only try from this box. Better than last start and can bounce back. LORRAINE JACKY (2) produced a modest effort most recently when sixth at this track over 400m behind Blessed Rain (23.01) in a Free For All. Has performed well from this box with a win and four minor placings to her name from nine starts. Must be included in calculations.",
